Usage: clonePlace [-help] [-clone_list {string1 string2 ...}]
                  [-master_inst <string>]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-clone_list {string1 string2 ...}     # cloneinst specification {<cloneInst1>
                                      # <orientation1> ...} (list, optional)
-master_inst <string>                 # master name (string, optional)